verbose_text: In the same species, the IP treatment with the PUFAs alpha-linolenate or eicosapentanoate decreased mRNA abundance of AgRP (alpha-linolenate) and increased mRNA abundance of CART (alpha-linolenate and eicosapentanoate) thus favoring enhanced anorexigenic potential, in a way similar to the effects elicited by oleate.
